milestones.description: Dennis Lillee has become the highest wicket-taker in ODIs with 48 wickets, going past Andy Roberts's 45
Greg Chappell has become the top scorer in ODIs with 1213 runs, going past Viv Richards's 1211
This is the lowest match aggregate (315) involving teams Australia & New Zealand in ODIs
